For second-hand goods and trash and treasure,
the Holiday ya Flea Market is a must.
the market only 3min walk from MRT Shandao Temple station exit 6.

This Taipei market is a hot tip and many locals scavenge there for a piece of designer clothing or interesting home wares.

Holiday ya Flea Market have been set up with clear eco-protection goals in mind that are great destinations for budget travelers to go treasure hunting.
created by residents in the surrounding neighborhood, which has about 30 stalls displaying quality used items no longer wanted or needed by households. You will find vintage, bags and leather goods, small electrical appliances and dishes,collectibles, bric-a-brac, recycled and full to the brim with stockpiles of secondhand clothing, and often something you did not know you needed—all in good condition.

every month market coordinated with festivals and special events, making the experience of browsing through a flea market seem like attending a theme party.
Since all of the markets mentioned so far are open to all members of the public, who can register to set up a stand, there are different sellers each time, so on repeat visits you will be presented with new surprises and new treasure to patiently dig out.

10% of the sales proceeds will be donated to the NPO "rabbitsos".

also have
Live music,handmade food,
Flea Market,Vintage,
Creatives Market,diy hand bouquet,
Swap Books x Scavenger Hunt
tarot fortune telling,
photography outing,
Stray rabbit charity bazaar/Adopt bunny..and more

Location▲B1F., No.10, Shaoxing N. St. Zhongzheng Dist., Taipei City(MRT Shandao Temple station exit 6 off)

FREE ENTRY!
Can't wait to see you there!

《Holiday ya二手市集》

再生x歡樂x社會企業

『辦二手市集的契機…..？』

從三個關鍵字說起..

關鍵字【一】「古董/二手」

因為熱愛尋寶的快樂，在國外總漫遊於各類跳蚤市場和特色二手小店中，
每次去逛都不知道會遇到什麼好物的期待，想趁早先別人一步翻找挖寶的心情，
跟個性攤主老闆你來我往討價還價兼交友的過程，
發現寶物的加速蹦蹦心跳…總讓人欲罷不能！

關鍵字【二】「愛兔」

養兔多年，身為兔奴一族愛兔是必然地，關懷流浪兔那(拉高音)~是必需地。
前些年回國時曾與動保團體辦過二手物品愛心義賣會，
很開心籌集到一些流浪兔的醫療及照顧所需，
此後也希望能繼續為流浪兔盡一份心力。

關鍵字【三】「社會企業」

看到社會企業這個新名詞是近年的事，因好奇而進一步去了解，原來
〝社會企業指的是一個用商業模式來解決某一個社會或環境問題的組織〞( )
Yes！找到了！這就是我們一直想做的事！
找到夢想的答案－社會企業。
我們的終極夢想是成立charity shop慈善商店，
為弱勢族群（ex.街友/中高齡失業/自立少年…）提供工作機會，販售所得扣除營運成本後捐出50%予公益團體幫助更多流浪兔。

《Holiday ya二手市集》 是踏上夢想的第一步。

等了那些年，中正萬華大安一直沒有真正以跳蚤市場為主的二手市集，逛過台北各個創意/二手市集感覺都偏向文創路線且攤位內容重覆性高，
像古著類很多攤感覺都是專業帶貨賣家，專業有專業的好處ex.衣服都整理過，
但相對的價格基本都固定，沒啥討價還價的餘地，
唔蝦米不好，只是總感覺少了點那種自己挖寶的樂趣，
而且常常今天跟明天逛兩地不同的市集卻發現相同的賣家與昨天看過的貨.....冏
這在有時特地騎車到比較遠的地方去逛市集時就會感覺就有點悶(・_,・")
於是，決定熱血一回！
豁出去辦正港以跳蚤市場為主旋律的二手市集！
希望集合大家的力量一起玩出精彩、充滿樂趣的《Holiday ya二手市集》。
斷捨離後那些有故事的舊愛、已經用不到的、忘記哪來的禮物贈品、搬家抽獎電器家具、古著古董老東西、難以定義…etc，
神馬都可以～什麼都不奇怪(只要不違法..你懂得)！

法國收藏家柯里爾的名言：「跳蚤市場是淘舊貨者和獵奇者的幸福所在」

讓我們一起用環保優雅的生活態度創造出獨具台灣風味的二手市集！
就像在法國參加跳蚤市場早已是不分男女老少的全民運動(還有很多觀光客(｡◕∀◕｡))，
醬子融入日常生活的二手市集才是《Holiday ya二手市集》所盼望地。
and為了讓活動更有意義，
每次活動除公益團體外的各攤位當日所得10%將一起捐出幫助流浪兔(台灣流浪兔保護協會or台北市愛兔協會擇一捐助)。

時間沖洗歲月，情感觸覺亦慢慢褪色—喜樂與悲慟、熱情與淡然、深情與矛盾…營役紛擾有時，卻可曾坦然透露？十七世紀在西方的激情浪漫，若今天以音樂湧現，心聲和應與感悟後的起伏思潮，又能否重新觸動纖細的情緒神經？
2017年適逢蒙台威爾第誕辰450週年，聲蜚合唱節將呈獻其登峰造極的第四、五、六冊《牧歌集》當中多首作品，包括《狠心的亞瑪麗莉》、《向星辰傾訴》、《艾利安娜悼詩》及《我是一個少女》等，音樂愛好者萬勿錯過。

What’s on your mind? 
Times might have washed truthful feelings away—our innermost outcries of joys and sorrow, passions and melancholy, love and complications.  Have your nerves been ever touched?  When the Monteverdi’s madrigals, songs of love and life once blossoming in the 17th century, are brought alive today and as we voyage across the intense drama and quests for human expressions in his music, our souls are bound to echo with deep hidden sentiments. 
A repertoire of Monteverdi’s madrigals, with some of his best works (from the magnificent Book 4, 5, and 6) including Cruda Amarilli, Sfogava con le stelle, Lamento d'Arianna, Io mi son giovinetta, is to be shared with music lovers as the world celebrates the 450th anniversary of Monteverdi’s birth.

5 Major Reasons to Promote More Vegetarian/Vegan Days (Vegetarianism/Veganism)

(1) 慈悲：戒殺，停止助造殺生共業。
Compassion: Please Stop Killing and Stop helping others to kill. 
Eating Meat = Killing animals!
Every life is precious. Respect Life, Please Do Not Harm or Kill other sentient beings!

(2)環保：畜養肉食動物是地球暖化的主因，占約80%的排碳量 。Go Green: Live stocks are the major cause of Global warming, it account for 80% of gas production that result of damage of our Ozone layers. It also produces more gas than transportation. 

(3)健康：諸多疾病是由肉食引起，攝取膳食纖維反而對人體助益更大。Health: Meat eating lead to high level of saturated fat which increase chance for Heart disease (stroke, heart attack) and Cancer, increase of fibers reduce many illnesses and help longevity/healthier life.

(4)文明：畜養與宰殺過程皆很殘忍，不是文明人類該有的行為。 
Culture: The cruelty of raising and killing the livestock/animals are not something a normal human being should behave. It is really not civilize the way we as human treating those animals, the way they lives, the hormone and drugs human inject in those animals are not acceptable.

(5) 世界飢荒: 地球上有將近十億人遭受飢餓和營養不良之苦，每年有四千萬人死於飢荒，其中大部分是小孩。儘管如此，世界上卻有三分之一以上的穀物不拿來供應給人吃，而是用來餵牲蓄。在美國，牲蓄就吃掉了70%的穀物收成。如果我們把穀物給人吃而不是餵牲蓄，就不再有人挨餓了。
World Hunger: Nearly about 1 billion people on earth suffer from hunger and malnutrition. 40 million people each year die of famine, most of them are children. Nevertheless, more than one third of the world's grain supply is not used to feed human, but to feed livestock. In the U.S., livestock ate 70% of the grain harvest. If we feed use those grains to feed the human rather than feed livestock instead, then there will be no one suffering from hunger.

「 成為你想在世界上看到的改變。」~甘地 
“Be the change you want to see in the world.”~ Gandhi

《巴勒斯坦大飯店》－偶物 x 記錄劇場系列* 
 《The Smooth Life》－Puppet x Documentary Theatre Series*
Dafa Puppet Theatre(約旦／捷克) 、 Rolling Puppet 滾動傀儡另類劇場 (澳門)

［第十六屆澳門城市藝穗節 | 16th Macao City Fringe Festival］
主辦 Organisor： 澳門特別行政區政府文化局  

英語演出(含少量阿拉伯語)，設中文字幕
演出時間約一小時三十分鐘，不設中場休息

《巴勒斯坦大飯店》講述胡辛.阿比（ Husam Abed）的個人成長故事。胡辛在約旦的巴夸難民營(Baqa’a refugee camp)*出生，在壓迫、貧困、飢餓中成長，與父母及兄弟姊妹相依為命，及後透過自身努力在敘利亞取得化學學士學位；可是他的身份令他必須直面他身處的政治環境，這種迫切啟發了他對藝術的追求，最終輾轉到了捷克布拉格修讀偶劇導演系碩士課程，決定以戲劇為自己發聲。
《巴勒斯坦大飯店》是胡辛自編自導自演的記實劇場（Documentary Theatre），透過偶物（Puppet and Object）作為媒介，以輕鬆的說故事形式（Storytelling）演繹他的成長經歷。演出過程中胡辛會同時為觀眾準備晚飯，在阿拉伯的音樂和香料氣味環繞之中，觀眾彷如置身阿拉伯朋友的家中，聽他把故事娓娓道來。

*巴夸難民營(Baqa’a refugee camp)於1968年設立，位於約旦首都安曼以北20公里，安置了約10萬名已登記的巴勒斯坦難民，是約旦境內最大的巴勒斯坦難民營。[資料來源: 維基百科]

創作、導演、演出：胡辛．阿比 
舞臺監督、佈景設計、技術操作：蕾可.迪克
戲劇構作：林婷婷
監製：趙七

17-21/1｜星期二至六｜20:00
21, 22/1｜星期六、日｜13:00 
演出地點：何族崇義堂（大三巴街35號）
每場觀眾名額：約15人

票價：
澳門幣 50 

-----------------
延伸活動 一：【特定社群藝術工作者工作坊】

工作坊為期三天，透過經驗交流、理論講解、示範、互動遊戲和實際操作，教授社區工作應用戲偶的技巧，讓學員發掘以偶物作溝通工具、融入教育及輔導工作的可能性。 
適合以社區為工作對象的老師、輔導員、社工、藝術工作者、有志投身相關領域或對戲偶藝術有興趣的人士。

導師：胡辛.阿比（Husam Abed）
胡辛.阿比畢業於捷克國立演藝學院劇場系戲偶及另類劇場導演碩士課程，Dafa偶戲劇團藝術總監，藝術團體”Flying Freedom Festival”創辦人及成員之一。除了從事戲偶演出名，胡辛亦長期與聯合國難民署合作，於約旦、巴勒斯坦、伊拉克、敍利亞等中東地區的難民營從事社區藝術工作。

日期及時間： 
13/1（星期五）19:00 – 22:00 
14/1（星期六）14:30 – 17:30, 18:30 – 21:30　 
15/1（星期日）10:30 – 15:00（連午休時段）

地點：外港青年活動中心 
名額：15人
語言：粵語、英語

-----------------
延伸活動 二：【藝穗評地2017】

承辦： 澳門劇場文化學會
合作單位： IATC(HK) - 國際演藝評論家協會(香港分會)

主題座談：“異鄉戲味──身體、記憶、勞動” 
異國煮家鄉菜，要原汁原味，還是入鄉隨俗？愈來愈多澳門劇團及藝術家，以自身故事為材，於海外創作演出。是次座談邀請數位不同面向的藝術家及劇團，分享他們出走異地的創作、駐場經驗，從澳門、布拉格、巴勒斯坦到印尼，從香港到丹麥、烏鎮，交換菜譜、五味雜陳。

日期：1月15日 
時間：16:00 – 18:00 
地點：何東圖書館 
語言：粵語、英語

講者：胡辛．阿比 Husam Abed（約旦）、 Rolling Puppet 滾動傀儡另類劇場 （林婷婷 Ten ten La 、趙七 Kevin Chio／澳門）、 小城實驗劇團 （ 黃詠芝／澳門）、俞若玫（香港）

Rolling Puppet 滾動傀儡另類劇場

主辦單位保留更改活動之權利。

============================
＊滾動傀儡【記錄劇場系列】

當代劇場的其中一個相當重要的趨勢，正朝向記錄劇場、社區／社群特定等方向發展，以這種藝術形式探討劇場在當今社會上的功能及使命，為此滾動傀儡另類劇場將呈獻〔記錄劇場系列〕。

第一炮遠赴捷克布拉格與當地著名當代劇場Archa Theatre合作，從距離與文化差異中審視作為80年代成長的澳門華人的身份，並於2016年11月在布拉格每年一度的文化盛事Theatre Night Festival 及Akcent International Documentary Theatre Festival 演出《Made in Macau 2.0》，及後將於2017年2月到香港及澳門巡演。

第二炮，與約旦籍巴勒斯坦偶師胡辛阿比Husam Abed和他的Dafa Puppet Theatre合作，於澳門城市藝穗節2017呈獻演出《巴勒斯坦大飯店》及【特定社群藝術工作者工作坊】；演出以偶劇形式訴說他在難民營出身長大的成長故事，為觀眾補足"難民"被主流媒體遺忘的人性面，而非新聞報導裏面的一個數字。

陸續將會有更多關於記錄劇場系列演出、創作大師班，敬請關注我們的專頁及event page，密切留意更多詳程及其他演出的資訊！
Rolling Puppet 滾動傀儡另類劇場

登記成為「大滾友」，獲取最新資訊：http://goo.gl/forms/qeM1g2NCBe

==================================
《The Smooth Life》
Puppet x Documentary Theatre Series*

Performed in English with some Arabic, with subtitles in Chinese 
Duration: approximately 1 hour and 30 minutes, no interval

A non-traditional documentary and puppet performance for a dozen of spectators with a culinary surprise at the end. Palestinian Husam Abed was born and raised in Baqa’a refugee camp* in Jordan. Around the table, while the food is being prepared, in a charming and evocative way he tells the stories of his family in the context of the political events in his country over the past 30 years, with objects, photos, maps, videos and good old storytelling... We hear stories about a life and experiences far away from our reality.  Husam creates an atmosphere for all senses.  At the table, art connects with life and creation mixed with realism.

*The Baqa'a refugee camp first created in 1968, lies 20 km north of the Jordanian capital Amman, and is home to around 100,000 Palestinian refugees who are registered as such with the United Nations.  It is the largest refugee camp in Jordan.  [Source: Wikipedia]

Creator, Director, Performer: Husam Abed 
Stage Manager, Set Designer, Technician:  Réka Deák
Dramaturgy: Lam Teng Teng
Producer: Kevin Chio

17-21/1｜Tuesday to Saturday｜20:00
21,22/1｜Saturday,Sunday｜13:00 
Venue: Macau Ho’s Clan Association

Price：
MOP 50 

-----------------------------
Extended Activities #1: 【Puppetry Workshop for Specific Social Arts Workers】

Through sharing, demonstration, theatre games, theory teaching and execution, a three-day workshop will introduce the techniques of using puppets in engaging communities, and let participants explore possible ways of utilising puppets as communication tools in education and counseling.

It is especially suitable for teachers who focus on communities, counselors, social workers, artists and people who are interested in puppet arts.

Trainer: Husam Abed
Husam Abed is a Palestinian puppeteer, musician and social worker living between Amman and Prague. Master of Directing for Alternative and Puppet theatre at DAMU – Czech Republic. Founder of Dafa Puppet Theatre/Jordan and Czech Republic. He has been performing and leading puppetry and storytelling projects for children and youth in many countries especially refugee camps and underprivileged areas in Jordan. He directed puppet performances, collaborated with artists from many nations. He developed his way of performing by mixing storytelling with puppetry. A member founder of Flying Freedom Festival in Poland, a member founder of Amman Theatre Lab.

Thematic Talks: Foreign Theatre – Body, Memory and Labour
Macao artists are having collaborations and staying overseas for creative works in recent years. Some of them are going to share with you their residential creation experiences overseas.

============================
*ROLLING PUPPET 【Documentary Theatre Series】

One of the important trend in contemporary theatre are Documentary Theatre, Social/Community arts, and Engaged Theatre, which try to find out the function and mission of theater in the modern society.  In respond to this neccessity, Rolling Puppet Alternative Theatre will present Documentary Theatre Series in the coming year.  

The first performance is 《Made in Macau 2.0》in Prague, followed by Hong Kong and Macao tour in Feburary 2017. The performance quests the changing identity of Macao as a cultural hybrid by reviving intimate family memories and confronting present reality.  It's was presented in November 2016 during the Theatre Night Festival and Akcent International Documentary Theatre Festival in Prague.

The second project will be the visit of Husam Abed from Dafa Puppet Theatre, Jordan and Czech Republic.  We will present his solo performance《The Smooth Life》and a "Puppetry Workshop for Specific Social Arts Workers".   The performance shows how a refugee lives his life as a human, more than just a figure on the mass media.  This project will be part of the Macau City Fringe 2017.

More events, performances and Master Workshop of this Documentary Theatre Series will be announced.  Stay tuned with our Facebook page for updates!!

423219227738204.description:
Thời gian vừa qua thị trường bất động sản đã có sự khởi sắc rõ rệt,nhờ vào gói hỗ trợ nhằm giải cứu thị trường bất động sản của Chính Phủ Việt Nam mục đích để "cứu trợ người giàu".Thay vì để thị trường phát triển bền vững - ổn định thì các chủ đầu tư, môi giới, nhà đầu tư đã lợi dụng sự khởi sắc này đẩy giá lên cao, bong bóng trước đó còn chưa tan nay lại thêm lớn hơn.Cho nên bong bóng bất động sản sẽ xảy ra là điều tất yếu.


Theo một nhà môi giới có thâm niên cho hay:
Dự án phân lô bán nền của bên em chủ yếu bán cho nhà đầu tư kiếm lợi nhuận bằng cách " mua vào chờ chủ đầu tư lên giá và bán ra", chứ người mua nhu cầu thực gần như không có hoặc rất ít.Anh này cũng cho hay nguồn cung căn hộ chung cư  từ giá rẻ đến cao cấp hiện nay rất nhiều và những người mua chủ yếu là người đầu tư mua bán kiếm lời chứ người nhu cầu thực không có khả năng mua.
Cũng theo ông Trần Du Lịch  - nguyên Phó trưởng đoàn Đại biểu Quốc hội TPHCM : “Không có chính quyền, nhà nước nào lại đi giao đất cho doanh nghiệp mà không có đường đi. Rồi yêu cầu làm đường để tăng giá trị lên để bán. Đáng lẽ nhà nước phải làm cơ sở hạ tầng trước để nâng giá trị rồi mới giao đất. Chúng ta đang làm ngược lại. Chưa kể, thị trường nhà ở của chúng ta như chuyến máy bay toàn hạng business, không có hạng economic dành cho người ít tiền... Tôi nghĩ bong bóng bất động sản đã trở lại và sẽ nổ tung là đúng với quy luật của nó"



Bong bóng bất động sản nổ tung năm 2017


Theo ông Richard Leech - Giám đốc điều hành CBRE, giá nhà ở VN trung bình cao gấp gần 30 lần so với thu nhập, trong khi khoảng cách tương đương tại các nước Châu Âu là 7 lần, Thái Lan là 6,3 lần và Singapore là 5,2 lần
Cũng Theo ghi nhận của CBRE : Dù giá nhà đất giảm giá 50%, người mua vẫn e dè vì những người có nhu cầu thực thì không có tiền.Và hiện nay hơn 60% căn hộ đô thị hoàn thiện chưa có người ở.
Chúng tôi sẽ tiếp tục ghi nhận và cập nhật thông tin mời quý vị theo dõi!
Hãy chia sẻ thông tin hữu ích này đến mọi người nhé.

This Event Has Been Created To Help You Understand Petitions,and Petition Sites.
We will be discussing in depth: How to recognize a good petition and petition site, their functionalities and limitations. We will teach you how to write a viable petition, and how to properly seek out your targets. You will learn how to write a proper letter to Lawmakers, and really anyone you want to influence. 
This is not a cake walk, but you will be glad you learned it, because suddenly your eyes will be wide open to some truths that will make your life and the lives your trying to save, so much better. 
Much of this has been gone through, in T.A.R.A. https://www.facebook.com/groups/T.A.R.ATheAnimalRightsAssembly/  
There is still much to learn, and many of you have missed a great deal, and we will be going through that process together. 
R.O.A.R  https://www.facebook.com/groups/ROAR4TheVoiceless/
expressed a strong desire to lead their group through this process we are going through, and started an event, in alliance with us, and as their group is closed, I asked we re-start it in an open group, where all could attend and the owner kindly agreed, so that ALL ARA's would have full access. Please for the love of Animals, the Earth, your own well being, join us in this process, because 95% of petitions are proven to not hit their target, and I am going to show you why. Your attendance and participation will be greatly appreciated,and will be necessary for this event to be successful. You are encouraged to invite,and to share what you have learned. You are encouraged to ask questions. 

Welcome to this very special event hosted by two very special groups, that want to work together to make a massive change in a massive Global and catastrophic problem of epic proportion and utmost urgency. We are running out of time, and as petitions are the weapons you activists have chosen to utilize, it is time to sharpen your swords,and polish your shields. You will fight with your minds, and knowledge is the key to all great things before you, and it is the only way to win this war. No war was ever won without a great strategy. This is part of ours.

RULES: Leave your egos at the door, and pack up any racist, political, or religious misconceptions. Do not post just for the sake of posting, it should be on topic, or the topic will be buried. Be respectful, if you feel you cannot, take a break and leave the discussion until tempers cooled. Thank you.

You are the soul of the Earth 
You are Earth Keepers 
You ARE the warriors these times call for.

Λίγα λόγια για την ΕΥΡΥΝΟΜΗ
Mία από τις παλαιότερες θεότητες και σύμφωνα με τον 
πελασγικό μύθο, θεά των πάντων που προέκυψε από το 
πρωταρχικό Xάος. Eκείνη διαχώρισε τον ουρανό από τη 
θάλασσα κι έπλασε από το Bόρειο Άνεμο το σύζυγό της 
Oφίωνα με μορφή φιδιού. H Eυρυνόμη έφερε στον κόσμο 
ένα Aβγό, το οποίο χωρίστηκε στη μέση δημιουργώντας τον 
ήλιο, τη σελήνη, τα άστρα, τα βουνά, τα ποτάμια και τα 
ζωντανά πλάσματα. Tο ζευγάρι κυριάρχησε στον Όλυμπο 
μέχρι τη στιγμή που η Eυρυνόμη γκρέμισε τον Oφίωνα στα 
βάθη της γης και δημιούργησε τους Tιτάνες και τις Tιτανίδες 
και τον Πελασγό, τον πρώτο άνθρωπο, που προήλθε από 
τη γη της Aρκαδίας.
Όταν κυριάρχησαν ο Kρόνος και η Pέα, η Eυρυνόμη 
αποσύρθηκε στη θάλασσα, όπου εκεί μαζί με τη Θέτιδα 
υποδέχτηκε τον Ήφαιστο όταν εκείνος εκδιώχθηκε από 
τον Όλυμπο.
Mετά την επικράτηση των Oλύμπιων θεών παρουσιάζεται σαν 
κόρη του Ωκεανού και της Tηθύος. Mαζί με το Δία γέννησε 
τις Xάριτες (Aγλαΐα, Eυφροσύνη, Θάλεια).
H Eυρυνόμη είχε έναν πολύ παλιό ναό και γιορτή στη Φιγαλεία
της Aρκαδίας στις όχθες της Nέδας ή Nέδης. O ναός της 
υψωνόταν στη μέση ενός δάσους από κυπαρίσσια. 
Eκεί φυλασσόταν το λατρευτικό άγαλμα της που την παράσταινε 
σαν γοργόνα, από τη μέση και πάνω με τη μορφή γυναίκας 
και από τους γοφούς και κάτω ψάρι.
- Βιβλιογραφία - πηγές 
Απολλώνιος ο Ρόδιος, Αργοναυτικά, 1
ἤειδεν δ' ὡς πρῶτον Ὀφίων Εὐρυνόμη τε
Ὠκεανὶς νιφόεντος ἔχον κράτος Οὐλύμποιο·
ὥς τε βίῃ καὶ χερσὶν ὁ μὲν Κρόνῳ εἴκαθε τιμῆς,
ἡ δὲ Ῥέῃ, ἔπεσον δ' ἐνὶ κύμασιν Ὠκεανοῖο·

485787124965258.description:
徒步大吉岭，远望珠穆朗玛峰 （ Mt Everest ) 与 干城章嘉（Kanchendzonga）。

大吉岭国家公园----------Singalila这条徒步线，鲜少东亚徒步客，几乎都是印度人和欧美游客， 卻是颇受西方游客喜爱的偏休闲徒步线路，沿途设施也很完善，无须露营，差不多也是tea house trekking的模式。

这条线可以看到的著名的雪山包括：向前看，是世界第三高峰干城章嘉峰；向右看，可远观位于中国和不丹交界处的卓木拉日；向左看，依次是洛子峰、珠峰（东坡）、马卡鲁和珠穆朗卓构成的喜马拉雅高峰群，以及三姐妹山。

茶原与峦峦雪山叠在一起，走累了天冷了喝杯大吉岭奶茶，人生最休闲莫过于此。 

出发日期 Date：07-16/03/2017
费用 Tour Fee： RM 3500 pax ( 六人价，价格或会因人数、或大幅度汇率更动而调整）
付款户口： PBB 4436182324 TOH CHIN HONG 
email: happyletstour@gmail.com 
航班： Kuala Lumpur- Kolkata 

Itinerary 
Day 1 : Kuala Lumpur to Kolkata ( calcutta ), Free and Easy 
Day 2: Kolkata to Bagdogra by domestic flight. Free and Easy in Bagdogra prepare for next day trekking 

Trekking 6 days 

Day 03 : Darjeeling - Maneybhanjan 2134m by private car - Trek to Tumling, 3070m 11km trek.
After an early your breakfast our driver and guide will come to pick you at 9:00 am drive from your hotel to Maneybhanjang (34 kms, 2 ½ hrs drive your starting point of trek. the maneybhanjang altitude At 2134 meters, and also know as village of tribes people between india and Nepal border where the clients have to entry a pasport and India visa, Today you will trek up to the Tumling Ridge which is 11km trek from manaybhanjang through the Buddest monastary,local village, rhododrendon forestand, reach your destination for the day - Tumling - in 6-7 hrs. your overnight stay in a comfortable private lodge at Tumling.

Day 04 : Trek from Tumling (2940m) - via Kalapokhri - Sandakphu (3636M) 21km Trek 7hrs.
Early wake-up for a sunrise view from Tumling Top. Weather permitting you will get fabulous views of both Singalila and Chola Ranges. of Mount Kanchenjunga. Return to Tumling for breakfast and after breakfast take the trail through the Singalila National Park - via Gairibas - Kalipokhari to Sandakphu. The trail leads one through bamboo glades and farmlands with quaint little villages inhabited by warm and friendly people. it is a continuous climb through the rhododendron forests. the Distance from tumling to kalapokhari is 15 kms and it takes 5 hrs walking to Kalapokhari. our lunch at Kalapokhari after lunch we contineous our trek to bikhey vanjang which leveled 2km then steep up through the rhododendron and pine tree forests toward to Sandakphu, Distance is 4 Kms .Overnight at comfortable private loge at Sandakphu which is heighest point 3,636mt and 12500ft of your singalila ridge trek.

Day 05 : Sandakphu (3636m) – Phalut (3600m) 21km 7hrs.
Morning sunrise call to watch the pink, red and finally golden glow of sunlight as it inches its way East to West across the face of the Himalayas.
Sandakphu - Phalut. Resume trekking after breakfast from Sandakphu to Phalut (3600 meters). It is one of the loftiest peaks in the Singalila Range and Sandakphu to Phalut is the most spectacular of the trek. The burned silver fir forest makes a most beautiful sight. A walk of 4 hrs from Sandakphu you will come across a stone house with its roof blown off on the top of a small ridge. The place is known as Sabarkum and is 14 km from Sandakphu. Halt overnight at Phalut trekker hut. (please note this night we will provide the room in trekker hut we don’t have any chose because it's very remote place. 

Day 06 : Phalut - (3600m) to gorkhey (2500m) 14km 5hrs.
Phalut is most beautiful place in the whole trek. When we stepped out of the hut at dawn the valley below us one side is filled with clouds. The sun peeped through the clouds flowing into the Valley like river down and around the hill. The trek today from Phalut to Gorkhey from where we temporarily say goodbye to the views of Kangchenjunga and the eastern Himalaya and is another beautiful day of walking through rich forests of Rhododendrons and Magnolias with great birdlife. Finally we reach to Gorkhey a nice village the place for eco- tourism.

Day 07 : Gorkhey (2500m) - Timburey (1800m (13km 6hrs Trek.
Morning sunrise call to watch the pink, red and finally yellow awesome views after breakfast trekking via Samandin to Ramam Trekkers about 5 hours trek till the trail reaches the meeting of two streams called Gorkhey Khola.It's a picture postcard place. Resume trekking via Samandin to Ramam so this day we stay overnight at private home stay Timburey.

Day 08 : Timburey – Rimbeek - Darjeeling 6km trek (2020m) and drive 4hours to Darjeeling.
After your breakfast Trek from Timburey to Rimbeek via Srikhola village is almost level walk for the first 9 km. reaches Rimbik. your lunch at Rimbeek later we meet with vehicles and drive to Darjeeling 4hours Overnight at your Hotel in Darjeeling onward your journey. Free and easy 

Day 09: Bagdogra to Kolkata by domestic flight. Free and Easy.
Day 10: Back to Kuala Lumpur 

Cost Includes
- domestic flight 
-All necessary paper work and permit in Mountain and National park entrance Permit fees.
-All expenses for guide including
-Meals (Breakfast, Lunch and Dinner) during the trek.
any hot drinks like tea cofee water
-Accommodation during the trek at guest house/lodge.
-Local English speaking mountain guides lincensed holder
- Porter ( 2 person sharing 1 porter)
-Private Transport friendly local driver
-Arrangement of Sleeping bags with innerline provided by company 
-Group Medical kit box

Cost Excludes
-International Flight KL to Kolkata 
-lunch and dinner in Kolkata and Darjeeling 
-Personal nature of expenses such as laundry, telephone call, battery recharge, shopping, laundry, extra porters, beverages etc.
Tips for trekking staff and driver. (Tipping is expected, but it is not mandatory)
-Your travel insurance
Insurance which covers, medical, emergency evacuation, lost, theft expenses.
-Clients Personal gear and expenses for the trek.
-Additional costs or delays caused by management out of control like landscape, bad weather condition, in case of itinerary modification with a view to safety concern, illness, change of government policy, political instability raises strike, moment etc.
(Please Note : Porters / horse ---If trekkers would like to book personal porters for carry their luggage for the whole trek at, it will charge extra cost INR 6000/ per porter .) for 6 days.

SUPERMARKET
Designer Market in Vilvoorde.

From Friday 16th until Sunday, December 18th, you can find SUPERMARKET at Firma, a different view on a designer Christmas market. Perfect timing for those still looking for Christmas presents for friends and family. Or for yourself, of course.
 
Drinks, blankets, pillows, cookies, posters, pins ... Just like a real supermarket, you will find this and much more at SUPERMARKET. It’s not just a market where every designer has his own booth, but a real shopping environment where you will find an interesting mix of fun, upcoming brands and objects.
 
Cantine, the in-house lunch bar of Firma, will be there to spoil you. On Friday night you can enjoy the Late Night Opening with wintry drinks and snacks. For this special encounter Cantine will serve Danish craft beers from brewery to øl. On Saturday and Sunday you can reserve a table for breakfast, brunch or lunch. Cantine will serve pancakes, quiche, toast, cake and much more.
 
SUPERMARKET is a project by Baroness O.
 

Where?

     Firma - Schaarbeeklei 636 - 1800 Vilvoorde

When?

     Friday 16.12 from 11h to 23h

     Saturday 17.12 from 10h to 18h

     Sunday 18.12 from 10h to 18h

571701019694195.description:
FULL MOON JÓGA : SÓLRÚN MARÍA : RAGNAR ÁRNI

Með lækkandi sól og meðfylgjandi vetri er alveg tilvalið að kíkja í vinyasa jóga tíma til þess að losa aðeins um álagið sem að fylgir jólaönnunum. 90 mínútna hlýr jógatími sem að er krefjandi og fjörugur á sama tíma. Tímanum er svo lokað með afslappandi teygjum og slökun þar sem að Ragnar Árni leiðir okkur inn í dásamlegt ferðalag inn á við með aðstoð hljóðfæra og söngs. 

SÓLRÚN MARÍA ætlar að leiða jógatímann á þessu fullu tungli. Hún er útskrifuð fá Absoulute Yoga Academy í Thailandi sem hot yoga kennari. Serían sem að hún lærði heitir Fit Flow Fly og er hönnuð af Briohny Smyth og Dice Ilda-Klein, handstöðusnillingum. Þar af leiðandi er jógað sem hún kennir byggt á undirbúningi fyrir handstöðu og ýmsar handjafnvægisstöður. 

RAGNAR ÁRNI mun heiðra okkur með nærveru sinni að þessu sinni. Ragnar er 27 ára tónlistarmaður og læknanemi. Ragnar hefur tekið þátt í íslenska tónlistarlífinu sem saxófónleikari með ýmsum hljómsveitum þar á meðal Bubba, Hjálmum, Berndsen og Ásgeiri. Nú stígur hann sín fyrstu skref með sitt eigið verkefni undir nafninu RAGNAR sem söngvari og lagasmiður.

Fulla tunglið í desember er gefur okkur tækifæri á að líta aðeins inn á við. Með orku þessa tungls fylgir kjörið tækifæri til þess að skoða sjálfið. Þetta er tíminn til þess að auka sjálfstjórn og aga. Á þessum tíma er nóg af freistingum og því er mikilvægt að standa við þau gildi sem að við höfum sett okkur sjálfum. 

Komið og njótið með okkur á fallegu kvöldi í desember. Tíminn hentar öllum! Byrjendum sem og lengra komnum.

Skráning er hafin undir solir.is - fyrstur kemur, fyrstur fær dýnu! 
Verð er 2.200 krónur fyrir meðlimi og drop-in's

Hlökkum til að sjá ykkur á dýnunni í jólaskapi ! :) <3

577165495815533.description:
白天與黑夜；古典與現代；類比與數位；粗糙與細緻；安全與危險；秩序與瘋狂……Transition，是轉換，也是過渡。始於底特律，一路蔓延至伯明罕、柏林等地，作為不斷變異、具有多層切面的Techno類型，將狂熱和壓抑、明亮及深沉等看似對立的衝突性，藉由不同唱片騎師的創意巧思，每深入一層，就更能彰顯其自由轉換的本質，進而透過你舞動的肢體，引爆用文字難以訴說的真實情感！

Days and night; classic and modern; analog and digital; rough and tender; safe and dangerous; steady and crazy…It’s so conflicting, so mysterious, and becomes the true essence of this techno party “Transition.” From Detroit to Birmingham and Berlin, techno, as an ever-changing and break-free genre, have had the infinite possibility due to passionate devotions of many innovative DJs worldwide. 

德國指標性夜店Tresor創辦人Dimitri Hegemann曾說：「藝術是不讓城市陷入百般聊賴的唯一關鍵。」而這場以聽者為主角的互動藝術，怎能錯過你的融入及參與？即便在台北的周末夜晚，你依舊能感受宛如置身底特律工業兼具浪漫的迷離氛圍，享受一場放鬆有趣、毫無設限的Techno Party，救你脫離沉悶無聊的苦海。

Dimitri Hegemann, the founder of the nightclub Tresor in Berlin, has said, “Art is the only key to cities and localities not becoming boring and dangerous.” You don’t have to be in exotic lands for experiencing this kind of free atmosphere; just immerse yourself into the Detroit-and-Berlin style, raving Transition party at PIPE in Taipei, and you will be surprised and saved from the utterly dull and boring modern life.

若你還沒有來過PIPE，甚至第一次聽聞Transition，不用感到遺憾，更不必擔心猶疑。在這裡，沒有制式的框架，只有誠摯的邀請；信任你的心，更要信任你的耳朵，進入直覺與邏輯的灰色地帶，拋棄一切束縛掌控，讓自己在都會叢林中，隨著Tech電氣節拍狂舞、縱情於Minimal反覆迴盪的鼓聲、面帶Acid酸氣四溢的微笑，回歸靈魂深處的原始悸動！

Don’t worry if you have not heard PIPE or Transition before. We sincerely invite you to join this party—no limits, no boundaries. Let go of your logical mind; prepare yourself for techy rhythm, minimal drums and crazy acid sounds. Let’s get unconscious & have some fun!

DJ Line Up
ANTHANY (DB Studio)
DATABASS (EarWorn)
GUANJUN
VERTIGO (RebootTaipei)
YEN (SomaTaipei)

關於 DB Studio
成立於2012年，這個團隊包括DJ，ＶＪ，音樂家，編曲家， 音樂製作人，音響燈光設計師，藝術家，攝影師，舉辦的跳舞音樂活動主要以台灣的ＤＪ為主 ，當然不乏國際品牌的音樂合作，像是 DJ Bone，Technasia等等 期待透過整合讓音樂，表演，藝術等等元素能打造出創新的派對氛圍，融入生活之中。

這四天工作坊內容, 是Drunvalo集合過去之十多年教導和研究之精萃所在。導師會帶領學員，藉由不同練習進入“心之神聖空間”喚起“我是誰”的記憶。並與“生命的源頭”連結, 覺察我們的內在世界有如外在世界一樣真實。

~ 開展“心之神聖空間”之旅

ATTRACTIVE EXHIBITION !!
“ La flamme ” exhibition of jewelry&photography
tmh. × SHUN OKUBO × Aya Yamamoto 
2016. 12. 9 fri. - 12. 25 sun.

12/9(金)から25(日)の期間、恵比寿の Tmh.&L'INTERIEUR にて、ジュエリーブランドのtmh. 、SHUN OKUBO、そして写真家の山本郁による展示を行います。

tmh.×SHUN OKUBO×Aya Yamamotoの第三回目の展示となる今回は、“ La flamme ” をテーマにそれぞれの自由な解釈で展開する新作を展示、販売いたします。

tmh.は、前回の展示 “Re-naissance” に引き続き15世紀にメディチ家と対立したパッツィ家に纏わる逸話をもとに想起した架空のホテル “Hotel 1478” のためのグッズを制作。ホテルからイメージした新たなアイテムが登場します。

SHUN OKUBOからは、すべてのアイテムに“赤”い珊瑚を用いた“Cayenne”（カイエン）、K18 Yellow GoldとPlatinumのチェーンを用いた“Eternal Sunshine”、それぞれのリングにまつわる様々な架空の物語を秘めた７本の指輪からなる“Seven Stories”。３つの新しいコレクションが登場します。

山本郁の写真作品は、フランスの哲学者・思想家であるガストン・バシュラールの著書「火の精神分析」と「蝋燭の焔」にインスピレーションを得た、鮮烈な赤から繊細な赤まで、蝋燭の炎や煙の揺らぎを写した新作の写真シリーズです。

写真とジュエリーによる “ La flamme ” にみなさま、ぜひお越しください。

623369894491793.description:
Itinerary:
D1,	KL-多哈   KL--Doha          QR861   01:10—04:50 
多哈-布宜 Doha-- Buenos Aires QR773   08:10-21:00 
专车前往国际机场接机，送至酒店休息。
A bus will pick you up from the airport and send you to the hotel	/	飞机巴士

D2, 	城市游
布宜著名风景区老虎洲游览 
早上09:00分，专车从酒店出发前往布宜著名风景区老虎洲Tigre，搭乘10.30时的游船/包船，行驶于错落有致的，私人船坞林立的度假别墅之间，领略素有“南美威尼斯”之称的巴拉那河(Rio Parana)流域的Delta三角洲独特风景。午间返回市区。下午城市观光：游览国会广场，七九大道，独立纪念碑，五月广场，世界三大剧院之一的科隆剧院（外观）,总统府(玫瑰宫), 布宜诺斯艾利斯大教堂，博卡区及探戈的发源地Caminito小道，Puerto Madero(新港)及典雅的女人桥。
行程结束后，至酒店住宿休息。
自选项目：探戈秀/普通席/含晚餐
晚上20.30时，专车前往Tango Porteño观看闻名于世的阿根廷探戈表演，并享用阿根廷烤肉，体验阿根廷人的都市生活，极尽艺术和美食享受。结束后，送回酒店休息。
City tour,visit famous scenic spot -Tigre
At 9:00 am, the bus will drive from hotel to Buenos famous scenic spot-the Tigre. At10.30am,take the boat cross the private dock between forest of vacation home where you can appreciate the special scenery of Delta.Rio Parana is also known as the "Venice of South America. Back to downtown at noon.
We will have a city tour in the afternoon: visit parliament square, 'Avenue, Independence monument, Plaza DE Mayo, Colon theater, one of the world’s three big theaters (appearance), the Presidential Palace (Rose Palace), Buenos Aires Cathedral, Caminito trail which is the birthplace of the tango and Boca, Puerto Madero bridge (Newport) and elegant Woman Bridge.
After the trip, drive to the hotel to have a rest.

Option: Tango show/ordinary seats/dinner
At 20.30 PM, take a special bus to Tango Porteno to watch famous Argentine Tango performances and enjoy the Argentine roast meat. You will experience the Argentine city life and enjoy the best art and food. After that, we’ll drive back to the hotel.	

D3, 	布宜—火地岛  AR1852  EZE--USH  09:10—12:45
早上06:30时，从酒店出发，专车前往国际机场，搭乘AR1852赴火地岛。
抵达后，专车接机，送至酒店，酒店休息或自行游览火地岛镇中心区。
自选项目：直升飞机或滑翔机俯瞰世界最南端岛屿以及山川，时长1小时。
Buenos Aires - Tierra del fuego 
Start from the hotel at 06:30 am and take bus to the international airport. Take AR1852 to Tierra Del Fuego.
After arriving at the airport, a bus will pick you up and send you to the hotel. Have a rest in the hotel or visit Tierra Del Fuego downtown. 
Option: Take the helicopter or glider to overlook the world's most southern islands, mountains and rivers within one-hour.

D4, 	8：00 出发前往火地岛国家公园参观, 参观约4.5小时，下午13：30结束。（费用包含火地岛公园门票，不含小火车费用。）
15: 00 出发至码头，准备登船。
17：00离开乌斯怀亚，船长举行欢迎仪式，讲解探险和注意事项。邮轮将沿着著名的比格尔海峡和风景秀丽的麦金利通行航行。
We will drive to visit Tierra Del Fuego national park. It will take 4.5 hours to visit the park and ended at 13:30. ( Include: Tierra del Fuego park tickets, Exclude: small train costs.)
Arrive at the port at 15:00 and prepare to embark on the cruise.
Leave Ushuaia at 17:00. The captain will hold a welcome ceremony, giving you an introduction about the exploration and the matters needing attention. The cruise will navigate along the famous beagle channel and beautiful McKinley.

D5,	穿越德雷克海峡
Cross Drake Passage	

D6,	穿越德雷克海峡
Cross Drake Passage	

D7,	登陆南设得兰群岛
南设得兰群岛是野生动物的天堂。广大企鹅聚居地，有南极软毛海豹和南部海象统治海滩，这是个神奇的岛群。
Embark on the South Shetland Islands
The South Shetland islands is a paradise for wild animals. The penguin rookeries, Antarctic fur seals and walrus ruled south beach. This is a magical islands.

D8,	登陆南极大陆
在南极大陆的Peninsula's登陆，这个登陆点有着非凡的历史，有早期的探险相关的探险小屋和早期捕鲸船遗址。您将能够登陆探索其冰山惊人的风景，雪，冰，山川河流，以及令人难以置信的野生动物种类繁多的原始荒野。除了企鹅和海鸟你很可能近距离看到威德尔海豹和小须鲸，驼背鲸。 
   Land on the Antarctic Peninsula. The landing site has a special history. There are early expedition huts and early whaling sites. You will be able to explore its breathtaking scenery, snow, ice, mountains and rivers, and incredible wildlife varieties of pristine wilderness. In addition to the penguin and seabirds you probably can get close to see Weddell seals, Minke whales and humpbacks.                                                                                                                                                                  	

D9,	登陆巴布亚企鹅聚集地和南极科考站（英国）及博物馆
穿越NEUMAYER 海峡和LEMAIRE 海峡，登陆参观巴布亚企鹅聚集地和英国南极科考站及博物馆和正在使用的南极邮局，在这里你可以购买南极纪念品和寄明信片。
Land on Papua penguin colonies and Antarctic research station (UK) and museums
Across the strait NEUMAYER and LEMAIRE channel, land on to visit Papua penguin colonies and the British Antarctic research station and museums and the post office. Here you can buy souvenirs and postcards at the South Pole.

D10,	离开南极洲跨越德雷克海峡。
在甲板上我们的讲师和博物学家为我们寻找海鸟，鲸鱼以及享受一些专题讲座。以放松的方式总结过去几天探险生活，并颁发登陆南极证书。
Across the drake passage and leave the Antarctica
Our instructor and naturalist will help us look for birds, whales, and you will enjoy some lectures on the deck. After making a conclusion of the adventure life over the past few days in forms of relaxation, we’ll issue the approval certificate of landing on the Antarctic.

D11,	跨越德雷克海峡
Cross Drake Passage	

D12,	跨越德雷克海峡后到达火地岛。
Cross Drake Passage and arrive at Tierra del Fuego	

D13,	火地岛—卡拉法特  AR1691  USH--FTE  14:15—15:37
船上用过早餐后，8：30 到达火地岛码头。
参观火地岛监狱博物馆，约2个小时。
12：00 专车送至火地岛机场。
抵达后，专车接机，送至酒店，酒店休息或自行游览卡拉法特镇中心区。
Tierra del Fuego - Kara Falt 
After breakfast on the ship, we’ll arrive at Tierra del Fuego dock at 8:30.
Visit the museum of Tierra del Fuego prison for about 2 hours.
We’ll sent you to Tierra del Fuego airport at 12:00am.
After arrival, a bus will pick you up and sent you to the hotel, have a rest at the the hotel or visit Carla Falt downtown.	

D14,	专车游览冰川国家公园
早上8：00出发，行程约7小时。
自选项目：下午进入当地巴塔哥尼亚特色农庄，参与剪羊毛、骑马、收树莓等活动，了解当地风土人情，含烤肉晚餐。
Visit the Glacier National Park by bus
Start to go at 8:00 in the morning and drive about 7 hours.
Option: go to a characteristic Patagonia farm in the afternoon and participate in sheep shearing, horse riding, raspberries and other activities. You will know the local customs. Barbecue supper included.	

D15,	卡拉法特-巴里罗切  AR 1691  FTE-BRC  16:25-18:10
上午游览Laguna Nimez国家公园（Bahía Redonda，Lago Argentino）专车参观游览阿根廷湖周边湖光山色迷人风景，火烈鸟、天鹅、灰嘴鸭等鸟类环绕湖边，国家公园各种特色鸟类和花草根据季节变化呈现出缤纷景色，行程约3小时。
午饭后，15：00专车送机至卡拉法特机场，飞往巴里罗切。抵达后，专车接机，送至酒店休息。
Carla, Barry has AR 1691 FTE - BRC also - afar off
Visit the Laguna Nimez national park (Bahia Redonda, Lago Argentino) and take our bus to visit Argentina lake and charming scenery, flamingos, swan, ash mouth, ducks and other birds around the lake. Special species of all kinds of birds and flowers and plants present a colorful scenery according to seasonal change in the national park, It takes about three hours to visit the park..After lunch, we’ll send you to Carla airport at 15:00, and fly to  Bariloche. After arriving there, we’ll pick you up and sent you to the hotel.	

D16,	专车游览Circuito Chico+维多利亚岛及红皮树林
早上09.00时，从巴里洛切酒店出发，全程60公里，呈现了Nahuel Huapi湖周围最重要的大自然风景。第一次去巴里洛切游玩，Circuito Chico几乎必然是首选，不仅是因为这个地方代表了山脉风光，而且能够在半天之内认识并且爱上这个城市。游览约3个小时。
约12.30时，专车从酒店出发，前往Pañuelo港口，首先坐船30分钟，到达位居中央地区的Anchorena港口，是维多利亚岛最窄的部分，也是服务中心。可以选择徒步的小路很多，边走边欣赏岛上的每个角落，美丽的景色，丰富的历史，壮观的自然环境，这样的散步就是一种享受。接下来，再坐船到达Quetrihue群岛，岛上有世界上唯一的红皮树林。这种树可高达15米，花为白色，果实为紫色，树干粗壮，树皮细冷，为桂皮色。1980年被宣布为国家公园，这里水天一色，耳边是鸟叫虫鸣，水波潺潺。尘世的喧嚣已经远离，如画如诗的纯净美景，叫人怎能不陶醉其中。整个行程约4个小时。行程结束后，专车送回酒店休息。Take our bus to visit Circuito Chico + Victoria island and Red-skinned woods
Start from Bariloche hotel at 09:00 in the morning. We’ll drive for the 60 km where you can see the most important nature scenery around Nahuel Huapi lake. Circuito Chico is the must-see place if you visit Bariloche for the first time not only because this place represents the mountain scenery. You will fall in love with the city within half a day. About three hours’ visit. Start from the hotel at 12:30 and drive to Panuelo port. Firstly, we’ll take a boat for 30 minutes. And then arrive at Anchorena port in the central region which is the narrowest part of Victoria island as well as service center. There are many paths where you can have a nice walk and enjoy every corner of the island, including the beautiful scenery, rich history and magnificent natural environment. Such a walk is a kind of enjoyment. Next, take the boat again to go to Quetrihue islands which have the world's only Red-skinned woods. The tree can be as high as 15 meters. Its flower is white and the fruit is purple with thick trunks, in cinnamon color. It was declared as a national park in 1980. Here the water has the same color with the sky. You can hear the sound of bird and the rippling of water. You have been away from the noise of the outside world and enjoy the picturesque scenery. The whole trip will takes about four hours. After that, drive back to the hotel	

D17,	巴里罗切-布宜 AR 1675  BRC-AEP  11：55-13：58
巴里罗切小镇城市游，可参观各种特色巧克力店。
午餐后，搭乘专车到达机场，抵达布宜后，专车接送至机场，搭乘航班回国,结束您的行程。
布宜-多哈 Buenos Aires – DohaQR774  23:25-23:15 
多哈-KL   Doha - KL         QR860  02:50-15:00
Bariloche – Buenos
Bariloche town city tour. You can visit the various characteristic chocolate shop..
After lunch, take our bus to the airport. After arriving in Buenos Aires, transfer to the airport and take flight back home. The end of your trip.	

D18, 经转机回到自己的祖国 
Back to motherland after flight transfer.

So because of numerous issues with the previous arrangement we've made an alternative plan for a Xmas party to remember (or not) depends on how much lemonade is consumed!  Christmas Jumpers are almost without doubt a necessity!!!
PLAN: (People can join in at any stage along the journey) 
Part 1, 
2pm  as Big Ben strikes, 2 teams set off on a Christmas themed hunt (Obvs there will be a prize for the winning team) and during the course prizes can be won (Think Dale Winton's Supermarket Sweep) for completing random challenges for example, photo with a police officer (thats too boring to be a real one). 
Part 2, 
For those who want to something that will resemble a Christmas dinner there is an option around 5-6pm to eat (timings/food is flexible). 
Part 3,
Finish up at Winter Wonderland and let the magic continue.

Only numbers we need are for those who would want to eat, if you want the dinner let us know by commenting as pubs/restaurant are rammed so we've got to be decisive and take whatever booking times we can. The rest is flexible as people can just tag-a-long at any point.

Dress Code: Business Casual or Retro outfit
*****Retro outfit not mandatory****

The Taiwanese Young Professionals & Entrepreneurs Association of BC (TYPEABC) is happy to welcome everyone to join our 2016 TYPEABC Annual Networking Gala! The purpose of this event is to allow attendees to meet new people, network, expand their social circle, and to interact with professionals from different industries. It will be hosted in a format where everyone can walk freely to mingle with others while enjoying finger food and refreshments. During the event, we will also celebrate the 14th Anniversary of TYPEABC and introduce our board of directors. About 120 people are expected to attend the event. We will have exciting live performances, games, and prize draws.

This year's Gala theme is "The Era: Retro Gala"! Wear your Retro Outfits and win prizes for best outfit!

台灣青年商會歡迎大家能共襄盛舉參加我們一年一度的社交晚會. 這次的晚會是為了讓參與來賓有機會認識新朋友, 擴張社交圈, 建立人脈, 並與各行各業的專業人士交流. 我們將採取自由走動方式讓大家更有機會互動! 活動當天我們也會慶祝青商會邁入第十四屆並介紹理事團隊. 在舉辦過程中, 我們會有節目表演、遊戲及抽獎，勢必空前的熱鬧. 人潮保守估計約 120人.

今年的晚宴主題是"跨時代復古風晚宴"! 穿上你的復古服裝，最好的裝扮將贏得獎品！註明: 並不強制規定復古裝

『BackpackFESTA2017』とは？
BackpackFESTA2017は、旅を夢見る全ての若者にふ贈る日本最大の旅イベントです。
世界中を旅した豪華ゲストによる旅のトークライブや、旅をテーマにしたコンテストのプレゼンテーション、旅ゴコロをくすぐられるショートムービー、豪華景品が当たる旅の抽選会など。旅への好奇心を刺激される魅力的なコンテンツをお届けします！
きっと、あなたの人生を変える、そんなイベントになるかもしれません。
過去6回、東京・大阪・福岡などで開催してきた、紛れも無く日本で最も大規模な世界一周イベントです。
2011年3月10日に第一回を開催した当イベントは2013年まで東京で開催され、2014年には大阪を、2015年には福岡を追加し、徐々にその規模を拡大してきました。
さらに今年は、仙台・名古屋・沖縄を加えた全国6都市で開催、総勢7,000人の来場者を予定しています。
過去2万人以上が参加し、数多くの若者がこのイベントから刺激を受けて世界中へ飛び立ちました。

為了迎接 Outofstock 邁進 10 周年，OUT OF CAFÉ 準備了一個新驚喜帶給大家。年初時我們專誠到日本拜訪了一位在料理界舉足輕重的「料理研究家」- Mr. Yusuke Hotta 堀田裕介先生，向他請教食物設計和製作的技巧，尤其學習日本人對製作每份食物的專注和一絲不苟的精神，務求將最高品質的食物帶給客人。除了華麗的食物包裝外，也包含了料理研究家對食物質素的堅持和執著。

堀田先生現在是大阪幾間著名餐廳的食物負責人，亦經常在日本不同地方舉辦大型食品活動，利用當地食材去推動本土的飲食創意和文化，希望令更多不同國藉和地方的人，能認識日本的飲食文化和精神。

今個 12 月，我們決定要將從堀田先生身上學習到的跟大家分享，非常榮幸能夠邀請到這位料理研究家親身來到 OUT OF CAFÉ 駐店，讓我們成為首間由堀田先生主理的海外 Pop-Up 店，將大阪 Smorrebrod kitchen / スモーブローキッチン 的餐單帶入 OUT OF CAFÉ。

Pop-Up 店只限兩天，座位有限，歡迎優先訂座: 2882 9116

【5次元的意識で理想の未来の自分を実現する】

今まで多くの方々が日時や開催場所により参加できなかった不便さを一気に解消するために世界中どこからでもいつでもInternetによるi- Counseling, Consulting, Coaching, Mentoring Serviceを提供することになりました。

そこで、世界中、どこからでも何時からでも参加できる【多次元で自分のコアを創るSelf Leadership with i- Coaching, Mentoring】を開始いたします。

FVA（Future Vision Achievement）のProgramをフレームワークとして使い、あなたの固有の課題や目的に沿ってごく贅沢なPrivate　Coaching & Metoring　Serviceです。

世界中、どこからでもFBのMessageでご相談ください。

尚、この期間中の面談希望者は東京で場所を指定しプライベート相談のチャンスを提供いたします。

・個別相談：日時は相談のうえ決定します。
・真剣に考えている方のみ受けさせていただきます。

FBの個人メッセージで必ずご趣旨を連絡ください。



多種多様な不安な材料が噴出している昨今、自分の基盤（コア）を未来から現在、そして過去まで自分の創造力で確固たる自分のコアを確立出来るとしたらいかがですか？

１．自分のIdentityが明確になり、過去のこだわりから決別し、自分に自信が持てる様になる。

２．未来の自分のVisionが明確になり自身に満ち溢れた自分になっていく。

３．人間関係においてぶれない自分になれる。

４．自分を多次元から観ることにより、じぶんのDefining Moments（決定的瞬間）から隠れていた自分を感じることが出来、未来ビジョンが明確になる。

５．激変する世界情勢や周りの変化に対応できる自信をもつようになる。

それは夢と勇気と希望にあふれるエネルギーの場を持つ自分になり、人間関係、仕事にも大きな意味を持って生きていける様になります。


＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿
ご希望の方は、FBの個人のMark Komatsuあてのメッセージでご連絡ください。

または日本では9日以降、０９０－１０３１－７００７にお願いします。

＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿

さらに　Relational Partnership,Creative Business Partnership, Servant Leadership Partnership そして多次元に繋がるUniversal Partnershipへと繋がるプログラムもあります。

先ずはSelf Leadershipで未来の自分を確立してみてください。

＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿

【小松　敬之（マーク・小松）のプロフィール】


【略　歴】
高崎工業高校卒業後、ロータリークラブ交換留学生として渡米、インディアナ州ベッドフォード高校を卒業、その後、インディアナ州にある米国名門校パーデュー大学の経営工学を卒業した。この大学で初めてのInternational Exchange Programを結成し、初代Chairmanとして就任。


Global 企業の日本法人の社長を兼務しながら、アジア担当役員の責務を果たし、アジア各国の会社・組織をいくつも設立・発展させてきた。　その間、Core(人間性）とCommunicative Relationship（心から分か合える関係）を基盤にビジネスを成功に導く人財を時にはカンセリングし、コンサルティングを提供し、彼らを成功に導くコーチングをしてあげる５C（Core, Communicative Relationship,　Counseling, Consulting, Coaching) コンサルティングを開発する。　


2000年を期に独立。米国、日本、アジアを中心に企業の経営者、幹部の経営施策とリーダーシップ開発による業績の向上支援に従事している｡　


個人の長所を伸ばして成功に導く、二代目社長継承、幹部の5Cエグゼクティブ　コーチングは定評がある。 小松のコンサルティングの特徴として、世の中の変化、内部組織の変化に対応するため、人間的側面に重心を置きながら、顧客の多様化に対する戦略とマーケティング、マルチプロセス対応型人財開発を指導・コーチングを行い結果として財務状況の改善を図るコンサルティング、エグゼクティブ・コーチングを実施している。


【ビジョン・ミッション】
自らUniversal Leaderとして進化・成長し続け、世界平和と人類の繁栄のために貢献できるUniversal　Leadersの創出を援助し世界の相互成長を続ける。


『世界に通用するUniversal Leadersを創出する』、FVA （ヒューチャー　ビジョン　アチーブメンツ）代表。 リーダーシップ　プログラムの開発と講師・コーチ
今までに、数百人のマネージャーと数十人の社長を創出してきた、りーダーシップ継承と人財開発に基づいた経営戦略の施策を提供するグローバル　　ビジネス　コンサルタント。


米国、日本、アジアにおいて経営者から幹部社員を対象に講演、セミナー、出版活動も行っている。
著書には、一瞬で人生が変わる！「自分のルール」の作り方、フォレスト出版、「世界一働きたい会社を創ろう」フォレスト出版。　人生の縦糸『Naked Core』ミライビジョン出版


日本コンサルタント協会理事及びグランド・マスター講師、５Cビジネス・コンサルタント育成集中講座開発者。
日本リーダーシップ協会 会長＆グランドマスター：　　リーダーシッププログラム開発者


ホノルル、ハワイ在住、日本、アジア、アメリカ間でコンサルティング・エグゼクティブコーチングを従事する。

726847970797176.description:
GUSTAVO MENDES EM: “ A T R E V I D O ”

Gustavo Mendes tem mais de 20 milhões de visualizações no YouTube. Sua interpretação da presidenta Dilma o transformou num fenômeno nas redes sociais.

"Gustavo Mendes ATREVIDO", mostra um artista mais maduro, com uma carreira solidificada e muitas histórias para contar. Gustavo tem muita experiência nos palcos e sabe deixar a plateia a vontade. Pode-se dizer que em ATREVIDO, ele quase se assume como um missionário da comédia, interagindo com personagens que por meio de um telão interferem no show, e com o público com muita intensidade.

Além dos personagens icônicos, Gustavo também vai interagir com outras entidades mais diretamente presentes na sua vida: sua mãe, seu analista, alguns dos seus amores, e pessoas comuns que querem saber da sua vida, dar dicas e sugerir caminhos.

Aliás, intensidade é a marca desse novo trabalho. Vamos ver um Gustavo que já conhece os atalhos do palco, que sabe a hora de gritar e a hora do silêncio. Mas que ninguém pense que faltarão os elementos que cativaram uma legião de fãs por todo o país: tem Dilma? Sim. Tem música? Muita música. Imitações? Claro! Porém, tudo num novo ambiente, autoral, com uma nova cara e principalmente, uma nova alma.  Gustavo Mendes cresceu e está mais ATREVIDO do que nunca.

SERVIÇO:

A T R E V I D O - GUSTAVO MENDES - CAMPO GRANDE 2016

743715332435346.description:
SCAA IDP講師培訓認證是一個為期一天半的專業講師培訓課程（教學理論學程），也是美國精品咖啡協會培養系統講師、考官的必修訓練。

教學內容主要涵蓋講師教學技巧、教學方式設計、學習成果評估與課程管理等培訓；也將介紹美國訓練發展協會(American Society for Training & Development, ASTD) 所發展的ADDIE模型，ADDIE是一套從分析(Analysis)、設計(Design)、發展(Develop)、執行(Implement)到評估(Evaluate)的教學原理，引導學員應用該成人學習方法在SCAA的系統教程上。此課程適合未來有志往講師方向邁進之學員，習得並應用這套理論在任何SCAA CAMPUS教育訓練上。

結訓後學員可獲得美國精品咖啡協會的助理講師認證（Lead Instructor Credential），並可在美國精品咖啡協會所策劃的課程或活動中擔任助理講師、累積資歷，以進一步往協會認證專業講師（Specialized Instructor）邁進。

★ 如何取得SCAA Specialized Instructor專業講師資格? 
請入SCAA官網：https://specialtycoffee.wufoo.com/forms/scaa-specialized-instructor-application/

日期：
2016年12月29 (四) 9:00AM ~ 17:00PM
2016年12月30 (五) 9:00AM ~ 12:00PM
地點：TCL台灣咖啡研究室
講師：Esther Shaw 

Esther Shaw 來自美國波特蘭是美籍華裔的咖啡人，曾在Intelligentsia Coffee & Tea 和 Dark Matter Coffee擔任首席品管與採購管理，也擔任過咖啡師大賽區域與國家選拔的評審，目前為SCAA認證專業講師，每年定期在台灣咖啡研究室教授SCAA認證課程。除了沉醉於咖啡搖籃裡，Esther本身也是名獨立樂團的音樂家，懷抱著音樂夢想，在咖啡與音樂的世界裡怡然悠游。

// S i t e B o d y E x p l o r a t i o n // 
// The Morava River – The Czech Republic / Moravia //

International Interdisciplinary Open–Air Workshop for dancers and artists exploring the relation among body, art and landscape led by Frank van de Ven (NL) and Milos Sejn (CZ)

The program will include:
• MB - (mind/body, muscles/bones) movement training
• practice of and reflection on physical and mental training
• walking and wandering, silent walk, pilgrimage and nocturnal journeys
• various modes of experiencing body, movement and landscape
• investigating divergent senses of space and time
• peripatetic records, drawing, writing, immediate contact with surroundings
• mental topography of a location, myth, archaic mind and genius loci
• geology, archaeology and history of Landscape as a model of self: layers, vertical connections and labyrinths

Participants profile:
for artists and advanced students working in performance, dance, landscape art, sculpture, photography, architecture, theatre, visual arts, biology and natural history.
Selection of participants will be based on c.v. and motivation.
No previous (dance) training is necessary but the workshop will be physically demanding. A good overall condition is required.

The number of participants is limited. We recommend early applications.

MORE INFO ASAP

810152995791934.description:
（Please scroll down for English）
阿三x煩惱詩社．文學x街道
實驗計劃@ A Walk with A3
　
日期：2016年12月7日至2017年2月19日
地點：Shop A3（銅鑼灣霎西街1號，即南洋酒店旁）
　
寫在前面
實驗，是未知結果又不一定有所謂結果、邊做邊構想從實戰中修訂再修訂的過程。既然這僅是街巷旁的一面牆與櫥窗，而當下生活急迫得只剩下疑問，我們便藉文學及藝術，給此地留下一點氣息。
巷，是城市的狹縫，經濟發展的後援，人們歇息的場所。那裡不只有烏煙瘴氣，還有人們以勞力換來的生計，及不能說清是否生活的生活。我們一眾過客，原來均與巷有過一段不盡相同的故事。巷所牽動的，是記憶和情緒。
文字充斥城市角落，文學卻摒棄於生活之外。我們仍然相信，能讀懂一首詩是件美麗的事，能懂得珍惜嘴巴吐出的話，是讓人堅定走下去的原因。觀看如同閱讀，是次計劃分為六個章節，跨橫兩個年度逐一上場。
　
目錄
7 Dec	我們曾在此停留
19 Dec	灣仔巷景：駱克道．菲林明道
27 Dec	灣仔巷景：聯發街．機利臣街
10 Jan	灣仔巷景：寶靈頓街．祥和里
23 Jan	生活狹縫裡所記掛的
6 Feb	灣仔巷景：A Walk with A3
　
仗義協力：徐沛之（Chui Pui Chee）、張偉樂（Cheung Wai Lok）、Raina、LXM、Harrison Chiu
　
www.awalkwitha3.com/
www.hkbobby.com/chansailok
www.facebook.com/Fannoupoem/

　
　
Chan Sai-lok x Fannou Poetry Society．Literature x Street
Experimental project @ A Walk with A3
　
Date: Dec 2016 – Feb 2017
Venue: Shop A3, No. 1 Sharp Street West, Causeway Bay (next to South Pacific Hotel)
　
Preface
Experiment, an explorative process leading to unknown outcome or nowhere sometimes, is all about contemplation, practice and revision, again and again. This exhibition space is merely a wall and a display window at the corner of an alley. While there is nothing but struggles and question marks left in today’s living, we leave a trace of flavor here with our literature and art works.
Allies are cracks in a city, nourishing its economics and accommodating its residence. There are not only untidiness and disorder, but also livelihood, if that can be called life, earned by hard working. Each of us, even as passerby, must have our personal stories with an alley which touches our memories and emotions.
Words fill every corner of the city, yet literature is an outcast of life. We still believe that reading into a poem is a beautiful thing; and cherishing the spoken words while reading provides the strength to live. As a visual/reading program, this project comprises six chapters which will be presented one after the other during the cross-year exhibition period.
　
Chapters

23 Jan	Memories from the slit of life
6 Feb	Alley View in Wan Chai: A Walk with A3

For second-hand goods and trash and treasure,
the Holiday ya Flea Market is a must.
the market only 3min walk from MRT Shandao Temple station exit 6.

This Taipei market is a hot tip and many locals scavenge there for a piece of designer clothing or interesting home wares.

Holiday ya Flea Market have been set up with clear eco-protection goals in mind that are great destinations for budget travelers to go treasure hunting.
created by residents in the surrounding neighborhood, which has about 30 stalls displaying quality used items no longer wanted or needed by households. You will find vintage, bags and leather goods, small electrical appliances and dishes,collectibles, bric-a-brac, recycled and full to the brim with stockpiles of secondhand clothing, and often something you did not know you needed—all in good condition.

every month market coordinated with festivals and special events, making the experience of browsing through a flea market seem like attending a theme party.
Since all of the markets mentioned so far are open to all members of the public, who can register to set up a stand, there are different sellers each time, so on repeat visits you will be presented with new surprises and new treasure to patiently dig out.

10% of the sales proceeds will be donated to the NPO "rabbitsos".

also have
Live music,handmade food,
Flea Market,Vintage,
Creatives Market,diy hand bouquet,
Swap Books x Scavenger Hunt
tarot fortune telling,
photography outing,
Stray rabbit charity bazaar/Adopt bunny..and more

Location▲B1F., No.10, Shaoxing N. St. Zhongzheng Dist., Taipei City(MRT Shandao Temple station exit 6 off)

FREE ENTRY!

《Holiday ya二手市集》

再生x歡樂x社會企業

『辦二手市集的契機…..？』

從三個關鍵字說起..

關鍵字【一】「古董/二手」

因為熱愛尋寶的快樂，在國外總漫遊於各類跳蚤市場和特色二手小店中，
每次去逛都不知道會遇到什麼好物的期待，想趁早先別人一步翻找挖寶的心情，
跟個性攤主老闆你來我往討價還價兼交友的過程，
發現寶物的加速蹦蹦心跳…總讓人欲罷不能！

關鍵字【二】「愛兔」

養兔多年，身為兔奴一族愛兔是必然地，關懷流浪兔那(拉高音)~是必需地。
前些年回國時曾與動保團體辦過二手物品愛心義賣會，
很開心籌集到一些流浪兔的醫療及照顧所需，
此後也希望能繼續為流浪兔盡一份心力。

關鍵字【三】「社會企業」

看到社會企業這個新名詞是近年的事，因好奇而進一步去了解，原來
〝社會企業指的是一個用商業模式來解決某一個社會或環境問題的組織〞( )
Yes！找到了！這就是我們一直想做的事！
找到夢想的答案－社會企業。
我們的終極夢想是成立charity shop慈善商店，
為弱勢族群（ex.街友/中高齡失業/自立少年…）提供工作機會，販售所得扣除營運成本後捐出50%予公益團體幫助更多流浪兔。

《Holiday ya二手市集》 是踏上夢想的第一步。

等了那些年，中正萬華大安一直沒有真正以跳蚤市場為主的二手市集，逛過台北各個創意/二手市集感覺都偏向文創路線且攤位內容重覆性高，
像古著類很多攤感覺都是專業帶貨賣家，專業有專業的好處ex.衣服都整理過，
但相對的價格基本都固定，沒啥討價還價的餘地，
唔蝦米不好，只是總感覺少了點那種自己挖寶的樂趣，
而且常常今天跟明天逛兩地不同的市集卻發現相同的賣家與昨天看過的貨.....冏
這在有時特地騎車到比較遠的地方去逛市集時就會感覺就有點悶(・_,・")
於是，決定熱血一回！
豁出去辦正港以跳蚤市場為主旋律的二手市集！
希望集合大家的力量一起玩出精彩、充滿樂趣的《Holiday ya二手市集》。
斷捨離後那些有故事的舊愛、已經用不到的、忘記哪來的禮物贈品、搬家抽獎電器家具、古著古董老東西、難以定義…etc，
神馬都可以～什麼都不奇怪(只要不違法..你懂得)！

法國收藏家柯里爾的名言：「跳蚤市場是淘舊貨者和獵奇者的幸福所在」

讓我們一起用環保優雅的生活態度創造出獨具台灣風味的二手市集！
就像在法國參加跳蚤市場早已是不分男女老少的全民運動(還有很多觀光客(｡◕∀◕｡))，
醬子融入日常生活的二手市集才是《Holiday ya二手市集》所盼望地。
and為了讓活動更有意義，
每次活動除公益團體外的各攤位當日所得10%將一起捐出幫助流浪兔(台灣流浪兔保護協會or台北市愛兔協會擇一捐助)。

853113901501823.description:
日惹婆罗浮屠（Borobudur）一入眼裡就是 萬丈森羅，萬佛朝宗之態，讓人嘆為觀止。不過日惹的美何其只是婆罗浮屠， 還有文遺prabanam 印度建筑、古風依舊的爪哇文化、生机勃勃的市井街头、悠哉閒哉的Dieng高原。 

過去我們在日惹谈宗教建筑和符号同，2017年我們調整行程還會在涼爽Dieng高原留宿一夜，清晨徒步看雲海，午間悠閒走茶原

如此精彩，决定去的话就算你有缘啦
日期：April 25, 2017 – April 29, 2017
价钱: RM 780. (六人成團出發，15人满团，不包机票， 汇率以1美元:兑3.9 - 4.2MYR为准， 若汇率变动太大，将会调整价钱）
押金：RM300
航班资料:
AirAsia KL- Yoj : 0945
AirAsia Yoj- KL: 17:15

不包括机票，伙食和门票
包括住宿，导游和交通
银行资料:
Account Name: TOH CHIN HONG 
Public Bank:4436182324
首日：日惹苏丹宫殿和城市导览。
抵达日惹后入住住宿点、午餐后為日惹市區一日遊。印尼虽然是共和国，卻因为历史的发展日惹依然保留了苏丹制。此外日惹保留了许多爪哇传统，被誉为爪哇文化之都。我们会探访苏丹的水之行宫，然后在当地的Batik村看蜡染的制作。晚间的用餐和逛街会是在日惹最著名的闹市--- Malioboro。

第二日：婆罗浮屠—Merapi 火山
本日是属于婆罗浮屠的，这个世界最大佛教建筑犹如一个地面上的曼陀罗，从底层关于佛陀故事到顶层的无相，代表佛教三个层次。我们会在结束后前往印尼如今还非常活跃的火山---Merapi， 看之前火山爆发后所留下的满目疮痍。

第三日：Dieng 高原：Sikadang 火山口、颜色湖和小镇游。（留宿一夜）
印尼爪哇岛上有许多，这些火山的喷发带来了灾难，可是肥沃的火山灰也带来了丰硕的农收。因此，这一天我们会一早驱车3小时前往Dieng 高原，了解火山地区的地理景观，当地人们怎么生活。

第四日：徒步小山看日出雲海、茶原走走
Dieng的Prau山有著中爪哇著名的雲海， 若是有心可以在日出前上山看看。 早餐之後，就在茶原休閒走走看看。 午間返回日惹

第五日： Prabanam ， —吉隆坡
早餐之后，前往印尼世界文化遗产之一七世纪的Prambanan古印度庙。路上我们会穿过连绵不断的田地。休息片刻準備回返吉隆坡。

Day 1: KL – Jogja City Tour 
pick up at airport and go for lunch. after lunch go for Jogja City Tours : Sultan Palace-Taman Sari-Jogja Sightseeing City Tour. Straight trip to the palace, as the kingdom of Mataram was built in 1757 and the center of Javanese culture. On Saturday morning 10am there is the traditional wayang kulit show, after the show, visit the lorong of making wayang kulit, and having a coffee for the break. 
After lunch, the next destination to visit Taman Sari, where one of the unique architecture in Jogja. Subsequent visits to the home industry batik / batik village. Bring to Malioboro for shopping. 


Day 2: Borobudur Temple – Mount Merapi - Sleiman Labuhan Merapi
Pick up at the hotel for Borobudur sunrise. Visiting Borobudur, one of the World Heritage Site and the largest Buddhist temple. After brunch back to hotel for the rest.  continue the trip at afternoon to see one of Indonesia’s most active volcanoes is Mount Merapi. 


Day 3: Dieng Plateau Tours : Sikadang Crater – Color Lake – Hindu Temple Complex ( Overnight )
Morning pick up at the Hotel. Go directly to Dieng Plateau, on the way to see the beautiful valley cleft, stopping at the sikadang charter than to color lake and vegetables plantations in the mysterious Dieng Plateau with lush forests, bubbling pools, lakes and colorful remnants shrine of Hindu temple . 


Day 4: soft trekking to Mount Prau ( optional) Tea Garden Visit and hot spring 
Mount Prau  is Located at Central Java, this mountain offers a great scenic mountain view with a minimal effort of hiking. Weather is so cold and fresh. To reach at the top of the mount you must wake up at 6am and hike almost 3 hours.  The scenery is so beautiful. Before you reach the top, you can see the teletubies hill. after breakfast we would visit tea garden and hot spring 
Back to Jogja City.


Day 5: Prabanan Temple
After breakfast pick up to visit to the impressive Hindu temple in Prambanan. Back to hotel for pack up and lunch. Free & easy until pick up to airport for departure.


Tour Cost includes:
-- 04 Nights hotel accommodation based on twin or triple room
-- Air-conditioned Transport through out the tour as per the itinerary. 
--01 night simple homestay in  Dieng 
-- Local tour guide on each destination
-- Arrival & Departure Assistance at Airport.
-- Daily breakfast
-- All fuel charge, Toll taxes, Driver allowance taxes etc
Price Not Including : Entrance Fee, Tour Guide, Hotel and Tiping

Tour Cost does not include: 
-- Air Fare
-- All lunch & dinners
-- All entrance fees
-- Ramayana Show 
-- Expenses of personal nature such as Laundry, telephone bill etc
-- Any Kind of Tips. 
-- Other meals and services not mentioned above.

872736196196872.description:
An introduction to the vibrant world of butoh through KAI-EN butoh method. The method is based on SU-EN butoh method, which is KAI-EN´s training background. The aim is explicitly artistic - to create a dancing and performing body.
No previous butoh or other dance training is required, though you are expected to work hard both physically and mentally.

The body is the centre of the work.
In butoh, the body and the consciousness are pushed towards an intention of becoming other - other living beings, organic processes and forces. 
Butoh evokes an intense relation with the world through all senses. Through this process the body's relationship to the world is shifted. The body and the space becomes alive.

KAI-EN´s work engage in the subtle but radical qualities of becoming.
Through erasure, withdrawal and surrender, the body’s conditions of existence in the world are shifted. 
At its core lies a desire to become landscape - the body´s co-existence with the ever-shifting, diverse and vibrant universe.


March 11-12  2017 					
10 am - 5 pm	
								
@						
C.off
Körsbärsvägen 9 nb 
Stockholm, Sweden 

Workshop fee: 1 000 SEK

Application deadline: February 1st

Send your application with a short description of who you are and your motivations to: 
info@kai-enbutoh.se

No previous butoh or other dance training is required, though you are expected to work hard both physically and mentally.


Butoh originated in Japan in the late 50´s, in Tokyo´s avant-garde movement. The main founder is considered to be Tatsumi Hijikata.  
It has since then developed and spread over the world through artists working closely to him and their students and groups. 
The work is transmitted from body to body in a teacher/student relation, yet developed through each artists work.

KAI-EN studied with Swedish choreographer and butoh artist SU-EN from 2005-2010.
Through her final examination and solo performance project About Face in 2010, 
she was given the name KAI-EN (SEA SHELL-GARDEN) which signifies the living link from SU-EN's body and SU-EN butoh method.

SU-EN is the pioneer of butoh in Sweden. 
She studied in Tokyo from 1988-1994 with the Tomoe Shizune & Hakutobo group where the legendary dancer Yoko Ashikawa was choreographing and teaching. 
The base of SU-EN butoh method was developed from the Shizune/Ashikawa method.


For further information, please visit: 
www.kai-enbutoh.se

923857431030716.description: كثر الحديث عن التقاعد المريح للبرلمانيين و الوزراء بالموازاة مع النقاش الدائر حول إصلاح أنظمة التقاعد و أزمة الصندوق المغربي للتقاعد .وقد ارتفعت عدة أصوات في صفحات الفايس بوك وعدة جمعيات تطالب بإلغاء هذه المعاشات وتعتبر العمل البرلماني » انتدابا و ليس و ظيفة » ووجب بالتالي « إلغاء هذا الامتياز وجعل العمل البرلماني واجبا وطنيا وخدمة للمجتمع » , أما أخرون , فيعتبرون أن هذه التقاعد شكلا من أشكال الريع و استثنائيا لكونه لايخضع لطرق الاحتساب الجاري بها العمل مع باقي الأجراء في القطاع العام أو الخاص , كما أطلق نشطاء دعوة للبرلمانيين للتخلي عن معاشاتهم وصلت صداها إلى قبة البرلمان . و لتسليط الضوء على أهمية هذا الموضوع , نقدم هذه المعطيات : معاشات البرلمانيين: يستفيد البرلماني الذي أكمل الولاية التشريعية (مدة الولاية 05 سنوات ) من معاش يقدر ب 5000 درهم صافية معفية من الضريبة على الدخل وغير خاضعة لأي تصريح , و يتقاضى هذا المبلغ مدى الحياة بغض النظر عن سنه ابتداء من نهاية الولاية . وقد حدد مبلغ المعاشات العمرية للبرلمانيين في 1000.00 درهم عن كل سنة تشريعية على ألا يتجاوز. , مبلغ المعاش 30.000 (ثلاثون ألف )درهم , كما حدد واجبات الاشتراك في 2900 درهم شهريا بالنسبة للبرلماني أو المستشار تقتطع من تعويضاته أخر الشهر ونفس المبلغ يؤدى من طرف مجلس النواب أو المستشارين ليحول المجموع إلى الصندوق الوطني للتقاعد والتأمين وهو تابع لصندوق الإيداع و التدبير (القانون رقم 04-35 بتغيير القانون رقم 92-24 المتعلق بإحداث نظام المعاشات لفائدة أعضاء مجلس النواب والذي تم تطبيق أحكامه على أعضاء مجلس المستشارين بموجب القانون رقم 99-53) هذا القانون ملزم و ليس اختياري , ويمكن لأعضاء الغرفتين الذين كانوا منخرطين في إحدى صناديق التقاعد قبل انتخابهم ( الصندوق المغربي للتقاعد بالنسبة للموظفين مثلا ) أن يستمروا في أداء واجباتهم للاستفادة منه مع بلوغهم سن التقاعد . ويمكن للبرلماني الذي لم يكمل ولايته لسبب من الأسباب أن يستفيد من معاش يحتسب على أساس المدة التي قضاها و التي يجب أن تكون على الأقل سنتين , أما إذا كانت أقل , فيمكنه استرجاع مجموع المساهمات التي اقتطعت له . كما حدد هذا القانون معاش البرلماني الذي أعيد انتخابه مرتين في 7000 درهم و 9000 درهم إذا انتخب للمرة الثالثة . الجدل الدائر حاليا في المغرب حول تقاعد البرلمانيين تعيشه الساحة الفرنسية منذ إحداثه سنة 1904 حيث عرف تعديلات في سنوات 1958 , 2003 , 2007 وأخيرا 2010 , وكان سن التقاعد من النقط التي شملها التغيير حيث تم رفعه من 50 سنة إلى 60 في إصلاح 2003 ليرفع إلى 62 تدريجيا في تعديل 2010 ( البرلماني الفرنسي لا يستفيد من المعاش حتى يبلغ سن التقاعد ) , كما همت تعديلات 2010 مبلغ المعاش الشهري حيث انخفض من 1600 أورو إلى 1200 أورو (أي انخفاض بنسبة 30 في المائة) . ورغم إلغاء عدة امتيازات في إصلاح 2010 , فإن الفرنسيين مازالوا غير راضين و يعتبرون أن الدولة مازالت سخية أعضاء الغرفتين على اعتبار أن 1200 أورو الذي يتقاضاه البرلماني في سن التقاعد بعد مساهمة ولاية واحدة (05 سنوات ) تتطلب من فرنسي عادي العمل مدة 40 سنة . معاشات الوزراء (أو تكملة المعاش ), يتقاضى أعضاء الحكومة ابتداء من نهاية مهامهم معاشا يقدر ب 39000 درهم بالنسبة للوزراء و 30000 لكتاب الدولة بغض النظر عن المدة التي قضوها في هذه المسؤولية شرط عدم توفرهم على مداخيل أخرى . أما إذا كان للوزير السابق دخل , فإن القدر الذي يصرف له يكون الفرق بين هذا الدخل و 39000 و كمثال على ذلك , الوزير الذي عاد إلى الجامعة كأستاذ بعد نهاية عمله الحكومي بأجر 20000 درهم لن يحصل إلا على 19000درهم كتقاعد أي الفرق بين 39000 و 20000 , لذلك يفضل البعض تسمية هذا المعاش بتكملة التقاعد، و لن يتقاضى أي درهم إذا كانت له مداخيل أخرى (أكرية , تجارة , أرباح أسهم ,,,) يفوق مجموعها 39000 درهم . في حالة وفاة الوزير السابق , يستمر ذوو الحقوق في التوصل ب 50 في المائة من المعاش أي 19500.00 درهم . للاستفادة من المعاش , وضعت مسطرة تفرض على المعنيين بالأمر الراغبين في الاستفادة من هذا المعاش أن يدلوا سنويا بتصريح للشرف للوزارة الأولى عن جرد لمصادر عيشهم , و هذا يفترض حسن النية لصعوبة التأكد من المعطيات , وحسب تحقيق نشر في الحياة الاقتصادية , فإن من بين 302 وزير الذين عرفهم المغرب منذ 1955 إلى 22 أكتوبر 2004 تاريخ نشر هذا التحقيق , 80 منهم فقط يستفيدون من هذا التقاعد بالإضافة إلى أكثر من 20 أرملة , من بينهم المحجوبي أحرضان الذي مر من عدة حكومات و الذي يتقاضى تكملة معاش قدرها 10200 درهم شهريا بعد خصم مداخيله الأخرى التي تبلغ 28800 , أما العربي عجول الوزير الاتحادي , فلم يتقدم بطلب الاستفادة . أما المستفيدين الأخرين , فلم نتمكن من معرفة أسمائهم ولا المبالغ التي يحصلون عليها علما أن عدد هم سيكون قد تجاوز 100 نظرا لتعاقب ثلاث حكومات منذ ذلك التاريخ (حكومة جطو 1و 2 و حكومة عباس الفاسي ). و يرى عدد من الملاحظين أن الامتيازات المتعددة لأعضاء الحكومة سواء خلال مزاولة مهامهم الحكومية كالتعويض عن التنقل للخارج الذي يقدر ب 2500 درهم يوميا مع العلم أنهم غالبا ما ينزلون ضيوفا إما عند زملائهم في حكومات الدول الأخرى أو عند السفراء , أو كمنحة المغادرة التي تساوي عشرة أضعاف الراتب الشهري و التي تصرف في نهاية الولاية وامتيازات سخية أخرى تؤمن لهم مستقبلا مريحا وتجعل بالتالي ضرورة مراجعة هذا النظام أمرا ملحا . إن السياق التاريخي و الاقتصادي (صدور هذا الظهير يهدف إلى تمكين الوزراء السابقين من العيش في ظروف جيدة بعدما وصل إلى سمع المرحوم الحسن الثاني أن أحد أعضاء الحكومة السابقين يعيش ظروفا صعبة ) يختلف كثيرا عن الوضع الحالي وأن الوزير حاليا يكتسب خلال عمله الحكومي تجربة مهنية إضافية وعلاقات تفتح له فيما بعد فرص تقلد مناصب و مسؤوليات بامتيازات و رواتب أحسن خصوصا إذا علمنا أن وزراء الحكومات الأخيرة إما رجال أعمال أو أطر عليا في الإدارة أو في القطاع الخاص . ويضيف هؤلاء أن الاستفادة من التجربة الفرنسية في هذا المجال ستكون مفيدة للمغرب حيث يحصل الوزراء السابقون على تعويضاتهم كاملة خلال 6 أشهر بعدها يفقدون كل امتياز مرتبط بعملهم الحكومي بما في ذلك الحق في التقاعد باستثناء الوزير الأول. المصدر : ادارة نيوز: تامير صالح

·٠•● 一場融合多元藝術文化的Psytrance音樂派對 ●•٠· 

❂ 有一群隱身在山林裡的精靈們，在月神的招喚下，每年以春為始的4月...樹木抽芽、春雷綻放之時，在平常寂靜的山林間，這一天...美麗的精靈們將為萬象之始的春天揭開序幕......

❂ 2017年春天我們一起在森林裡，聽蟲鳴鳥叫，追蜻蜓賞蝴蝶，溪水玩耍....與大自然和平相處。伴隨著充滿宇宙能量的Psytrance音樂，神乎其技的UV螢光裝置藝術創作....化為大地精靈一起舞蹈吧！創造屬於我們的月光奇蹟。在這充滿愛，歡笑，和平，分享的時刻裡，你會感受到Psytrance音樂文化與美麗部落嬉皮風裝扮...是多麼的神秘且自由～

❂ 串連多種與 Psytrance 音樂相關的戶外派對文化。由音樂說故事，展開一場奇幻旅程。音樂藝術/服裝藝術/身體藝術/裝置藝術。所有美麗的事物，都該讓它們相遇！

❂ This is not only a psytrance party but an arts party! Explore fashion, body panting, and a variety of visual arts inspired by hippie culture and psytrance music. 

❂ Experience an atmosphere of mystery, peace, and freedom, with lots of love and smile～

996527430451570.description:
Since established in the year 2011, Korean Language House put much effort in promoting the study ethos of Korean in order to deepen the understanding of local people towards the Korean culture. At this moment, Korean Language House has opened about 40 venues in Malaysia, the Korean classes are teaching in Chinese, English and Malay (using DSS teaching method, which all learners are learning at their own pace) to train more local talents who can read, write, listen, talk and translate in Korean language. Besides that, the number of people learning Korean language is tremendously increased, and of course, the demand of Korean books is increased too. Therefore, Korean Language House established the first Korean bookstore in Malaysia.  
The bookstore brings more than 10,000 new Korean books and second-hand books such as storybooks, comic books, novels, Korean textbooks, etc. Except the Korean books, the bookstore will continue to bring in more Chinese and English books with the Korean theme to implement the purpose of the Korean bookstore. In order to let the public know the delicate Korean storybooks, as well as to promote learning foreign language and the ethos of reading foreign language books, the bookstore open day of Korean Language House will be on Sunday, 18th December 2016. In addition to that, we would like to welcome the public to come at 9am till 5pm to experience the exotic scholarly atmosphere. On the open day, there will be Halal refreshments provided for free, Korean literacy course, Korean seal cutting, “searching books” game, information about travelling, working and studying in Korea, lucky draw and other activities as well. The address of the bookstore is 91-3 (second floor), Jalan USJ 21/10, UEP Subang Jaya, 47630 Subang Jaya, Selangor. For people who are taking the train, please get off at USJ21 station, a three-minute walk in the direction of Main Place Mall and you will be reached at the KLH bookstore where is directly opposite of Main Place Mall.
We’d like to welcome all of you to attend. All attendants will be gifted with exquisite red envelopes of the fusion of Korean and Chinese. For attendants who make a reservation online beforehand, you will have chance to win a mystery gift through lucky draw session. For people who are interested, please drop us an email to admin@koreanlanguagehouse.com and provide us your name, contact number and the number of attendant. If you’d like to know more information, please visit to www.koreanlanguagehouse.com or email to admin@koreanlanguagehouse.com or call 
number: 016-3533658.
996527430451570.name: Korean Bookstore Open Day 韓國書店開張

996722003718490.description:
主辦單位：空白鍵    Spacebar_Room　 Spacebar Studio
　

沒有名字的電影值得你一起渡過週末夜嗎？

就像學校課堂的電影，長途客運上的電影，
那些不過度期待的故事往往帶來超乎想像的感受，

想像簡單的五條線索，我們決定與她共度週末。

好人好事永遠不寂寞，就像好電影一樣。
　
　　
【文青不挑片  之  空白小鍵人約法三章】
　
1. 每周三公布提示。
周五晚間七點開始進場，八點整準時開播→放映結束後歡迎一起聊聊天

2. 為了保有大家觀看的品質，我們有入場人數限制。
人數滿了之後，鐵門就會放下來無法進場→只好下次再來跟小鍵人們一起玩了

3. 低消飲品一杯，禁帶外食。
有冷/熱飲、酒精/無酒精飲品→搭配電影最實在

A movie lover should accept every genre film as long as it's a good one! 

We hold secret cinema for movie hipsters who truly love films every Friday night. 

*The event starts from 8pm, and the door will be closed at 8, so don't be late! 
*Only 5 clues will be released before screenings
*Titles are always remained unknown, unless u guess it right! 
*No entrance fee, but there is one drink minimum spending 
*Seats are limited (up to 60), so please show up earlier 

Welcome to join us!
Enjoy films and meet new friends!
